Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.30,0:01:45.80,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Are you prepared, my dear girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.80,0:01:47.41,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Prepare to advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.41,0:01:47.87,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:48.78,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Advancing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.64,0:01:52.92,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Where is our allies?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.67,0:01:54.99,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Left, forty degrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.99,0:01:56.17,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Prepare to fire main cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.03,0:02:00.92,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Distance: 400.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.92,0:02:03.96,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Load the H.E.A.T. round!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.96,0:02:04.74,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:06.90,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Origa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:08.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:11.97,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}After being canned in this thing for three days, I'm not dying until I have a shower!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:14.61,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Target locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:15.54,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:24.94,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Direct hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.94,0:02:27.20,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Anna, signal the troops trailing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,0:02:30.29,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}One vehicle destroyed. Continue advancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.29,0:02:31.29,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:33.65,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Filicia, cover Anna please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:34.90,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}R-Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.31,0:02:40.68,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's flashing out there, but it's not thunder. Just relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:42.56,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:52.06,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Th-Three o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:20.35,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.91,0:03:25.64,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Second Lieutenant Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.73,0:03:42.49,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:49.58,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Bamboo strips!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:28.11,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Come on, Noel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.11,0:04:30.95,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It won't be clean if you don't wash it properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:53.98,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.39,0:05:01.48,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}While it gets cold in the winter, it's great that this building stays cool in the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:05.25,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Oh? Isn't it the Rio-senpais' turn to do the laundry today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:08.50,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}They're busy and asked us to swap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:09.48,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Whose is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.94,0:05:11.19,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Filicia-san's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:15.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She said she lost her appetite and told us to eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.87,0:05:19.25,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'll have it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.01,0:05:22.17,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:24.17,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Preparations for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:25.08,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.08,0:05:26.12,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:28.76,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's a sin to play with food!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:31.26,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I-I'm not playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:33.08,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Well, it's almost time for Obon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:36.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Huh? What's Obon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.01,0:05:37.90,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Fiesta des Lumières.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:39.62,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Fi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:44.49,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Fiesta des Lumières is an event unique to the southern part of Helvetia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:50.85,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}According to folk belief, the souls of the dead would return to the world of the living during the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:55.74,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Paper lanterns are floated down the river as a symbol to send the spirits back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:06:00.88,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}In some provinces, the festival is called Obon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:02.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Right. Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.01,0:06:03.45,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:09.24,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Oh? It's the same thing then!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.24,0:06:11.58,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Souls returning?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.06,0:06:15.88,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Wait, wait! What does that mean? Does that mean ghosts come back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.88,0:06:17.31,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}In a sense, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:18.68,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Paper lanterns?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.68,0:06:21.29,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That sounds lovely, in a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:23.81,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}We build bonfires back in my village, but-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:27.93,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}No way! People who have died go to heaven, and stay there forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:30.47,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Only the evil spirits remain loitering on earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:33.04,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What? That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:34.91,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But in Church...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:36.13,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.61,0:06:39.11,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Hey! Come and help out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:43.03,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}When did you two go shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:44.91,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Oh, those are...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:47.46,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}They looked good, so we bought them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:48.91,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}And these too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.71,0:06:59.91,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Is this fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:01.66,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}No, Pastor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:02.67,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:04.89,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm done!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:08.83,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Your dad and mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.83,0:07:12.57,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I see... it looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:16.51,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What? Even the Church acknowledges it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.51,0:07:18.33,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That Fi-whatever?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:19.51,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:22.28,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}If it was the Central Protestant Church, they would kick up a fuss,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:24.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}but we're in a rural area here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:25.47,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What a random answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:31.03,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}In my village, we would make horses and cows out of cucumbers and eggplants
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.03,0:07:34.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}as vehicles for our ancestors to ride on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:41.24,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}And to amuse our ancestors who had returned, we would all dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.86,0:07:45.69,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Are you both making them too, senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:46.45,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:49.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}We only watched last year but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:05.90,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's part of our job to attempt harmonious relations with the local residents after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:09.63,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}If you don't get too fixated on it, it's just another lovely festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:12.34,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Right, Filicia?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:27.67,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Filicia-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:36.24,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:37.49,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:39.49,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:41.17,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I just made a blunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.17,0:09:45.31,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But it's rare for Commander to be so clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:46.84,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Unlike Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:52.74,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Well, these last few days have been really hot, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:53.26,Sora no Woto,TS,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\an8\fad(400,400)\b0\bord0.85\pos(321,364)\fscx82.5\fscy113.75\3c&H652F01&}「Water Melon」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:55.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I haven't been able to sleep well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:57.63,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'll take a short break.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:05.52,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Filicia-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:09.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The Commander seems a bit strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:14.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She skipped her lunch, and then goes off to buy watermelons, ignoring our food budget?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:17.37,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}There must be reasons... even for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:22.43,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Still, I think I'll talk to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:23.25,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.34,0:10:27.84,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Everyone has things that they would rather not share.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.84,0:10:29.71,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Just leave her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.00,0:10:34.03,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.39,0:10:37.34,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Do you know about it, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:38.69,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I've seen the records.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.69,0:10:41.25,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I had a first hand account of the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.25,0:10:42.14,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:10:59.06,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Filicia...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.99,0:11:07.81,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\i1}Hold it steady. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:12.22,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\i1}There, there, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:19.31,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\i1}And then... a ghost that looked like the Commander appeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.61,0:11:29.17,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\i1}There were many creatures things in this ocean long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.17,0:11:31.05,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\i1}That's unbelievable, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.70,0:11:34.31,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\i1}Have you ever heard that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:37.24,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}They say the world is gradually ending...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.24,0:11:41.47,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}and eventually, all humanity will perish completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:45.36,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Those are just... rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:53.04,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But if it's true, then what are we fighting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:07.23,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.23,0:12:09.47,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.67,0:12:46.01,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Ideographs?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.01,0:12:52.19,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:57.44,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I really wish I could read your final words.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.31,0:13:00.49,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}This equipment...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:05.08,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Could you be from the old era?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:19.39,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Commander...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:22.70,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Second Lieutenant Origa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:24.00,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Martina...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:25.49,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Anna-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.77,0:13:28.36,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.36,0:13:29.66,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}...am I the only one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.59,0:13:34.65,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:36.61,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}...are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:39.13,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.66,0:13:44.34,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}There are still survivors in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:46.79,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.30,0:13:52.68,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:56.59,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.36,0:13:58.59,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:02.06,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}...we lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.08,0:14:05.16,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}...to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:08.46,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}We couldn't protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:11.00,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:32.69,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The world has ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:34.81,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:37.74,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You are the remnants...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.79,0:14:42.03,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The final remaining bubbles on the salvation of humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:44.28,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Mankind...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:49.78,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}For this world to regain it's former glory... is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:52.31,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Don't decide that on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.31,0:14:54.54,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But that is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.51,0:14:58.01,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}So, it's fine to let it end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.47,0:15:07.74,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}To live miserably in the dregs of the world, in despair... is simply too desolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.74,0:15:09.29,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}No. I don't want this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.75,0:15:10.66,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:15.00,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Is there meaning to surviving in a world like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:17.81,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.70,0:15:41.98,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:52.53,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I am here! I am alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:54.59,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Please! Please save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.73,0:16:17.94,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.24,0:16:22.30,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:26.53,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}If my unit had only arrived half a day sooner,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:29.63,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}this would never have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:32.90,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Your Highness, Imperial Princess Iria.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.40,0:16:41.13,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But I was a little surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.51,0:16:42.51,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.51,0:16:47.15,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Well, you ignored the Fiesta des Lumières last year, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.45,0:16:49.47,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What caused this change?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.22,0:16:51.67,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.02,0:16:57.45,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That's a nice color, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:17:01.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's made in Treize. I bought them when the market was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:06.18,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Amazing! It's fantastic. Just fabulous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.48,0:17:07.77,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:08.57,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:11.45,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Certainly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.04,0:17:15.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She meant everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.57,0:17:20.92,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I thought of protecting the country, the people, like she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:24.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But at times, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:27.41,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What meaning is there in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:34.21,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}So if she really does come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:36.71,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I want her to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:41.60,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That aside, what about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:44.09,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}They're all worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:49.05,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That's true. Admittedly, I may have worried them a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.35,0:17:50.75,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I fail as a Commander, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:52.75,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's not just them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:54.84,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Even I... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.28,0:17:56.05,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Um?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:18:01.03,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Anyway, don't bear the burden on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:03.23,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Even I can at least listen to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.17,0:18:05.74,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Thank you, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:08.69,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Then I'll accept your offer and speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:09.96,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.96,0:18:11.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.38,0:18:16.72,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm troubled that I've gained weight this summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:17.24,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.58,0:18:20.74,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}At this rate, I won't fit into my winter wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.38,0:18:23.69,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I heard that if you eat only watermelon, you can lose weight,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.69,0:18:26.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}so I thought of trying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.01,0:18:28.38,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What's the matter, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:32.38,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Are you still feigning ignorance?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:32.88,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:35.77,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That's because on the front lines at the battle at Area 21, you were-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.77,0:18:37.83,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:41.31,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Could you possibly be thinking that I was reminiscing about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:44.45,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Y-You're saying, you weren't?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:51.43,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:53.91,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Should we go too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:11.93,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You made one too, right, Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.93,0:19:15.43,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I-It's not like I believe in souls or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.43,0:19:17.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's a mission. A mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.32,0:19:18.50,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.50,0:19:21.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Who are you sending off, Filicia-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:24.23,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}My previous colleagues,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.03,0:19:28.03,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}and a soldier whose name I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:32.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}My saviors who helped me realize what is truly important.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:34.09,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Could those the people possibly be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.00,0:19:36.16,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Filicia-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:40.07,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}If you have any sorrows, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:43.76,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}...I might not be able to help at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.21,0:19:45.03,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.01,0:19:50.06,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It seems like I made you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:51.03,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.21,0:19:53.81,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.81,0:19:55.42,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That is too sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.56,0:19:58.71,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Even I want to worry about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.35,0:20:02.62,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Filicia-san, you always worry about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.62,0:20:04.62,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I always made you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:06.13,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I want to worry about you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.88,0:20:10.58,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Because I love you, Filicia-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:16.90,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I adore you too, Kana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:20.47,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Just remain the way you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.92,0:20:21.81,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.42,0:20:24.63,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Filicia-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:27.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You're always reminding me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:30.91,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}...not to fear putting feelings into words.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:35.45,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I think that is a wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.22,0:20:40.41,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Commander...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.57,0:20:45.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Filicia...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:46.61,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Even I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:53.43,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Oh, you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.25,0:20:55.87,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}How adorable...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:09.53,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Do come again next year, ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:18.05,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Dad... Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.03,0:21:31.55,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Mother... Elder Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:34.44,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That person is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:44.13,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Say, Rio, you were just asking if there was any meaning in this world, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.13,0:21:45.05,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.19,0:21:50.58,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Ever since I was the lone survivor, I had pondered on that a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.94,0:21:54.22,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Why only I survived?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.79,0:21:57.54,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}And if there was a meaning to it. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:57.97,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\3c&H27004D&}Listen up. You can't just space out like that. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:22:00.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}And then I realized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.04,0:22:04.72,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's likely that there isn't any meaning to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.35,0:22:08.99,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But isn't that lovely as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.49,0:22:15.36,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Because, if there isn't any, then we can find them on our own accord.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.93,0:22:21.52,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}And now, I've found mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.52,0:22:24.77,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The meaning for me being here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.73,0:22:28.61,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}And then even the Pastor too...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.61,0:22:29.75,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Even the Pastor?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.75,0:22:32.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}He just did it his way? And Yumina-neechan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.00,0:22:33.75,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Well, he was really bad at it, so Sister Yumina...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.54,0:22:40.64,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I definitely do not want them to suffer those emotions as I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.00,0:22:42.39,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.66,0:24:21.72,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Next time: Phone Duty. Announcement of an Emergency Situation.
